Comment: Hello those who like to follow annotated games I'm hoping to get good comments on this one.

in my passed annotations i started at 1350 elo and ive been steadily climbing with some bumps here and there, and as i climb i always like facing tougher opponents.  this is my third opponent in the 1700 range since my return and this also happens to be a revenge match in a tourny we are playing together,
my classic LSB exit,  This was our 2nd game where i lost the first after playing 43 moves even and then just straight out blundering to lose,

and like i previously noted ive learnt the blacks like to park their DSB on c5 so i dont need to do a2 that i love to do lol,
and my response to this is ne2 with a quick d4 depending on what my opponent plays next
